  <official_title>An Open-label, Uncontrolled, Single Center, Phase I/II Trial to Assess the Safety and Efficacy of Autologous Hematopoietic Stem Cells Transduced With MT-gp91 Retroviral Vector in gp91 Defective Chronic Granulomatous Disease Patients</official_title>
