  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety and efficacy of administration of
      autologous hematopoietic stem cells transduced with MT-gp91 retroviral vector for patients
      with X-linked chronic granulomatous disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
